Net-SMTP-TLS

Net::SMTP::TLS provides a similar API to Net::SMTP, while at the same time providing SMTP AUTH and TLS capabilities. The module is based on Michal Ludvig's smtp-client.pl script, which can be found at http://www.logix.cz/michal/devel/smtp.

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc Net::SMTP::TLS

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Net-SMTP-TLS

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Net-SMTP-TLS

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Net-SMTP-TLS

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Net-SMTP-TLS

